WEBVTT

00:01:58.584 --> 00:02:01.960
As compared to any other
plantation drives,

00:02:01.984 --> 00:02:07.304
these forests have 30 times more trees
that grow 10 times faster.

00:02:08.424 --> 00:02:11.280
Before planting a forest in any new place,

00:02:11.304 --> 00:02:15.400
we first make a list of the trees
growing in their natural forests

00:02:15.424 --> 00:02:20.000
and then classify them
as per their height.

00:02:20.024 --> 00:02:22.550
Natural forests have soil
that is usually damp,

00:02:22.654 --> 00:02:26.880
and they always have nutrients and
dampness for plants.

